---
import Layout from '@layouts/layout.astro';
import Block from '@components/block.astro';
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<Layout title="Open Positions - Chief Technology Officer">
  <main class="font-mono flex h-full">
    <Block class="border-t-0" showTopLeft={false} showTopRight={false}>
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <Block class="border-t-0 border-l-0 border-r-0 p-10 px-24" showTopLeft={false}>
          <button onclick="javascript:history.back()" class="flex flex-row">
            <Icon name="back" height={32} width={17} class="mr-4" />
            <h1 class="font-display font-thin text-3xl">Chief Technology Officer</h1>
          </button>
        </Block>
        <div class="flex flex-col px-24">
          <div class="flex flex-row">
            <Block class="basis-1/3 p-8">
              <h3 class="font-light text-2xl">Basics</h3>
            </Block>
            <Block class="basis-2/3 p-8">
              <p class="mb-4">Chief Technology Officer (CTO)</p>
              <p class="mb-4">[City, State/Country]</p>
              <p class="">
                ERKKEL is a dynamic and innovative [industry/sector] company committed to revolutionizing [brief description of your company's mission or
                industry]. With a talented team and cutting-edge technology, we are poised for exponential growth and global impact.
              </p>
            </Block>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-row">
            <Block class="basis-1/3 p-8">
              <h3 class="font-light text-2xl">Position Overview</h3>
            </Block>
            <Block class="basis-2/3 p-8">
              <p>
                We are seeking a visionary and experienced Chief Technology Officer (CTO) to lead our technology strategy and drive innovation across our
                organization. The CTO will play a pivotal role in shaping the future of our company, leveraging technology to enhance our products/services,
                streamline operations, and drive sustainable growth.
              </p>
            </Block>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-row">
            <Block class="basis-1/3 p-8">
              <h3 class="font-light text-2xl">Responsibilities</h3>
            </Block>
            <Block class="basis-2/3 p-8">
              <ul class="list-disc">
                <li>Develop and execute a comprehensive technology roadmap aligned with the company's strategic goals and objectives.</li>
                <li>Lead the software development team, providing mentorship, guidance, and support to foster a culture of excellence and innovation.</li>
                <li>
                  Drive product innovation and development, leveraging emerging technologies and industry best practices to enhance our competitive position.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Oversee the architecture, design, and implementation of scalable and robust software solutions that meet the needs of our customers and
                  stakeholders.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Collaborate with cross-functional teams to define requirements, prioritize initiatives, and deliver high-quality products on time and within
                  budget.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Stay abreast of market trends, technological advancements, and competitive landscape to identify opportunities and risks, and make informed
                  decisions.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Establish and maintain strong partnerships with external vendors, technology providers, and industry stakeholders to support business
                  objectives.
                </li>
                <li>Ensure compliance with regulatory requirements, data security standards, and best practices in software development and IT operations.</li>
                <li>
                  Provide strategic guidance and recommendations to senior leadership on technology investments, resource allocation, and risk management.
                </li>
              </ul>
            </Block>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-row">
            <Block class="basis-1/3 p-8">
              <h3 class="font-light text-2xl">Qualifications</h3>
            </Block>
            <Block class="basis-2/3 p-8">
              <ul class="list-disc">
                <li>Bachelor's or Master's degree in Computer Science, Engineering, or related field. MBA or equivalent business experience is a plus.</li>
                <li>
                  Proven track record of leadership and success in a senior technology role, preferably as a CTO or VP of Engineering, with at least [X] years
                  of experience in [industry/sector].
                </li>
                <li>
                  Strong technical background in software development, architecture, and system design, with expertise in [specific technologies, frameworks,
                  languages, etc.].
                </li>
                <li>Experience leading and scaling high-performing engineering teams in a fast-paced and dynamic environment.</li>
                <li>
                  Strategic thinker with excellent analytical, problem-solving, and decision-making skills, with the ability to translate business requirements
                  into technical solutions.
                </li>
                <li>
                  Exceptional communication and interpersonal skills, with the ability to build relationships, influence stakeholders, and drive consensus
                  across the organization.
                </li>
                <li>Proven ability to drive innovation, manage change, and deliver results in a highly competitive market.</li>
                <li>
                  Demonstrated commitment to diversity, equity, and inclusion, with the ability to foster a culture of collaboration, respect, and continuous
                  improvement.
                </li>
              </ul>
            </Block>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-row">
            <Block class="basis-1/3 p-8">
              <h3 class="font-light text-2xl">Benefits</h3>
            </Block>
            <Block class="basis-2/3 p-8">
              <ul class="list-disc">
                <li>Competitive salary and performance-based bonuses</li>
                <li>Comprehensive benefits package including health, dental, and vision insurance</li>
                <li>Flexible work schedule and remote work options</li>
                <li>Professional development and training opportunities</li>
                <li>Dynamic and collaborative work environment</li>
                <li>Opportunity to make a meaningful impact and shape the future of [Your Company Name]</li>
              </ul>
            </Block>
          </div>
          <Block class="flex flex-col p-8">
            <form>
              <div class="flex justify-end">
                <button class="bg-orange-600 hover:bg-orange-800 text-gray-950 uppercase font-bold px-6 py-2.5">Apply here +</button>
              </div>
            </form>
          </Block>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Block>
  </main>
</Layout>
